\c 150 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 150\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Faarfannaa Jajachuu Isa Guddaa
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyoon jajadhaa! Iddoo isaa isa qulqullaa'aa keessatti Waaqayyoon jajadhaa! Bantii waaqaa isa humna-qabeessa keessatti isa jajadhaa!
\m \bd 2\bd* Gocha isaa isa aango-qabeessaaf isa jajadhaa; akka guutummaa guddina isaatti isa jajadhaa.
\m \bd 3\bd* Sagalee fiinootiin isa jajadhaa; kiraaraa fi maseenqoodhaan isa jajadhaa!
\m \bd 4\bd* Dibbeedhaa fi sirbaan isa jajadhaa; mi'a ribuu qabuun, ululleedhaanis isa jajadhaa.
\m \bd 5\bd* Sibiila walitti rukutamee sagalee ol kaasuun, isa jajadhaa! sibiila walitti rukutamee sagalee guddaa dhageessisuun, isa jajadhaa!
\m \bd 6\bd* Wanti hafuura baafatu hundinuu Waaqayyoon haa jajatu! Waaqayyoon jajadhaa!
\b 
